	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually you need a better weapon NOW!<br><br>Save the reaver till post lvl 30 when it procs and damage caps are off.&nbsp;&nbsp;Till then get a faster weapon.  There is no point in having a slow weapon that hits for your damage cap when you can have a much faster weapon that will hit for the same amount.<br><br>I recommend getting a cheap fast 2hs for now some options:<br><br>Tower Guards Blade<br>Deathwatch Sword<br>Axe of the Iron Back (yup even this is better at your level)<br><br>At level 30-40 the Dark Reaver is good, but I bet if you bought 1 at lvl 15 you'll be upgrading it before then with either a Blade of Xelgoz or something a little better.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
